              <td style=\"text-align: center;\">7,700</td>\n                    <td style=\"text-align: center;\">27773</td>\n                    <td style=\"text-align: center;\">30/12/2026</td>\n                    <td style=\"text-align: center;\">€1.50</td>\n                    <td style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>€11,550.00</strong></td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr class=\"total-row\">\n                    <td colspan=\"7\" style=\"text-align: right; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>TOTAL (VAT EXEMPT - Export)</strong></td>\n                    <td style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>€36,190.00</strong></td>\n                </tr>\n            </tbody>\n        </table>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 8.5pt; margin: 5px 0;\"><strong>Product info:</strong> www.groupegaillard.fr/gants-non-steriles/332-gant-nitrile-sans-poudre-emilabo.html</p>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 8.5pt; margin: 5px 0;\"><strong>Packaging:</strong> 100 gloves/box • 10 boxes/carton • 70 cartons/pallet</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"section\">\n        <h2>📍 DELIVERY & PICKUP</h2>\n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td style=\"width: 30%;\"><strong>Incoterm:</strong></td>\n                <td>EXW (Ex Works) - Marseille, France</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td><strong>Pickup location:</strong></td>\n                <td>Le Dépôt de Méditerranée Transit, 455 Chemin du Littoral, 13016 Marseille, France</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td><strong>Destination:</strong></td>\n                <td>Lublin, Poland</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td><strong>Transport:</strong></td>\n                <td>Organized and paid by buyer</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td><strong>Pickup deadline:</strong></td>\n                <td><strong>Immediate pickup authorized upon SEPA payment receipt</strong> (same day if payment confirmed before 3 PM)</td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"section\">\n        <h2>💳 PAYMENT TERMS</h2>\n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td style=\"width: 30%;\"><strong>Payment method:</strong></td>\n                <td>100% SEPA bank transfer before pickup</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td><strong>Currency:</strong></td>\n                <td>EUR (Euro)</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td><strong>Amount due:</strong></td>\n                <td><strong>€36,190.00</strong></td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"section\" style=\"page-break-inside: avoid;\">\n        <h2>🏦 BANK DETAILS - SOCIÉTÉ GÉNÉRALE</h2>\n        <div style=\"border: 3px solid #003366; padding: 20px; background-color: #f0f8ff; text-align: center; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.8;\">\n            <p style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><strong>Account holder:</strong> VL MEDICAL SAS</p>\n            <p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 13pt;\"><strong>IBAN:</strong> <span style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: 14pt; color: #003366;\">FR76 3000 3033 1100 0503 3660 214</span></p>\n            <p style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>BIC/SWIFT:</strong> <span style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: 13pt; color: #003366;\">SOGEFRPP</span></p>\n            <p style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><strong>Bank:</strong> Société Générale</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"conditions\" style=\"page-break-inside: avoid;\">\n        <strong>⚠️ VAT EXEMPTION - MANDATORY CONDITION:</strong><br>\n        This invoice is <strong>VAT EXEMPT</strong> under EU export rules (Article 262 I of French Tax Code).<br>\n        <strong>BUYER COMMITMENT:</strong> The buyer undertakes to provide the <strong>signed delivery note (CMR)</strong> stamped by the carrier proving that the goods have left French territory and have been exported to Lublin, Poland.<br>\n        <strong>Failure to provide this proof may result in VAT charges being applied retroactively.</strong>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"section\" style=\"page-break-inside: avoid;\">\n        <h2>✅ GENERAL CONDITIONS</h2>\n        <ul style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; line-height: 1.6;\">\n            <li><strong>Sale:</strong> Complete lot only (33 pallets, non-divisible)</li>\n            <li><strong>Inspection:</strong> Authorized at warehouse before payment</li>\n            <li><strong>Validity:</strong> 48 hours from issue date</li>\n            <li><strong>Condition:</strong> New, original packaging, optimal storage conditions</li>\n            <li><strong>Compliance:</strong> CE medical device standards</li>\n        </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"section\">\n        <h2>✍ ACCEPTANCE</h2>\n        <div class=\"signature-box\">\n            <p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px;\">I, the undersigned <span class=\"signature-line\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>, acting on behalf of <strong>Medicov s.c.</strong>,</p>\n            <p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\"><strong>accept this proforma invoice under the stated terms and conditions, including the commitment to provide the stamped CMR delivery note.</strong></p>\n            <p>Place: <span class=\"signature-line\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Date: <span class=\"signature-line\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n            <p style=\"margin-top: 30px;\">Signature (preceded by \"Approved for order\"):</p>\n            <p style=\"margin-top: 40px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"footer\">\n        <p><strong>VL MEDICAL SAS</strong> • SIRET 853 225 100 00025 • Capital: €1,000</p>\n        <p>190 Rue Topaze, 13510 Éguilles, France</p>\n        <p>Phone: +33 6 18 24 40 13 • Email: jeanluc@aubagnac.com</p>\n        <p style=\"margin-top: 10px; font-size: 8pt;\">\n            This proforma invoice is not a final invoice and does not constitute a request for payment until formal acceptance.\n        </p>\n    </div>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774843623779}}
